================================================================================
Third-party dependencies and their licences
================================================================================

All runtime dependencies are open source (MIT, Apache-2.0, or BSD). No
proprietary SDKs, Google Mobile Services, Firebase, analytics or crash-reporting
libraries are used (Blueprint Section 6.2 / 6.4).

